               <msContents>
                  <summary>F<locus target="#1r">fols. 1r, </locus>-97r: Gospel of John, arranged for the days of the week by a later hand: Monday (1r), Saturday (15v), Tuesday (20r), Thursday (27v), Saturday (40r), Thursday (44v), Wednesday (48v), Thursday (and Friday is erased, 60r), Friday (and Saturday is erased, 77v), Sunday (89r). The መልአ is on <locus target="#97v">97v</locus>. </summary>
